				<div id="mw-content-text" lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr"><div class="dablink">This article is about the British charity.  For the American charity, see <a href="Comic_Relief_USA" title="Comic Relief USA">Comic Relief USA</a>.  For other uses, see <a href="Comic_Relief_(disambiguation)" title="Comic Relief (disambiguation)">Comic Relief (disambiguation)</a>.</div>
