<h3><span class="editsection">[<a href="../../w/index-title=Comic_Relief&action=edit&section=23.php.html" title="Edit section: 2013 event">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline" id="2013_event">2013 event</span></h3>
<p>The 2013 event will take place on Friday 15 March 2013.</p>
<p><a href="One_Direction" title="One Direction">One Direction</a> will record the official single, a cover of <a href="Blondie_(band)" title="Blondie (band)">Blondie</a>'s "<a href="One_Way_or_Another" title="One Way or Another">One Way or Another</a>". The single will go on general sale in February.<sup id="cite_ref-23" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-23"><span>[</span>23<span>]</span></a></sup></p>
<p>TV programmes that will lead up to the main event include:<sup id="cite_ref-24" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-24"><span>[</span>24<span>]</span></a></sup></p>
<ul>
<li><i><a href="The_Great_British_Bake_Off" title="The Great British Bake Off">The Great Comic Relief Bake Off</a></i></li>
<li><i><a href="Great_British_Menu" title="Great British Menu">Great British Menu for Comic Relief</a></i></li>
</ul>
